<item>
            <title>[SOLR-726] driver and datasources are not loaded using the multicore lib aware SolrResourceLoader</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-726</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;see &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nabble.com/dataimporthandler-and-mysql-connector-jar-td19146229.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://www.nabble.com/dataimporthandler-and-mysql-connector-jar-td19146229.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
The jar containing the (jdbc) driver have to be present in the java classpath. Putting it in coreX/lib or in the shared lib dir of a multicore solr doesn&apos;t work&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12403051">SOLR-726</key>
            <summary>driver and datasources are not loaded using the multicore lib aware SolrResourceLoader</summary>
